---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Tim Raysby">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">About</h1>

  <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-zinc-300 max-w-2xl">
    <p class="text-xl">I'm Tim. I'm an operator who builds AI infrastructure that runs on the machine in front of me — not in someone else's datacenter.</p>

    <p>Most of the AI economy is a tax on attention. I'm building the alternative: software that respects the two scarcest resources you have — your tokens and your time.</p>

    <p>By day I work as a senior engineer at a major insurer. Evenings and weekends I build NEXUS, my personal AI infrastructure. Everything you see here is built on it.</p>

    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">More to come.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
